Eco - Alonism / A Cry To The Moon                             

                            Trance | A State Of Trance 

             320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2013-10-21 | 00:13:35 | 31 Mb


ECO just doesn't do average. That's exactly what got him and his 'A Cry Out To The Moon' featured on Universal Religion Chapter 7. Set for release on the ASOT label, the New York based producer also provided a powerful B-side, the mighty 'Alonism'. A dream-team that carries the unrivalled ECO sound. The release of his 'Walkabout' and 'The Calm' got ECO warmed up for more - much more. This guy's clearly bursting with inspiration, walking the fine lines of brilliant trance and groundbreaking, deep and dreamy prog. His productions ever stand out, carrying something original. From the unique musical dream of 'A Cry Out To The Moon' to the playfully-minded 'Alonism', this is Eco doing what he does best.
